{"id":"da0821af-c488-4d1a-b504-e12266281ab4","name":"The Patron | Vivienne Delacroix","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>A Billionaire yandere bought your career, isolated you from everyone, and wants you forever.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 146, 234);\"><strong>\"That was me, darling. All of it.\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5wecW1uZa1PjdeIThCc2k.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(199, 146, 234);\"><strong>THE SETUP</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Two years ago, you were </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>nobody</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">A struggling artist drowning in student debt. Selling pieces for pennies. Three months behind on rent. Then the emails started. Anonymous commissions. Generous payments. A mysterious benefactor who </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 146, 234);\"><strong>loved your work</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">They paid triple your asking price. Connected you with galleries. Funded a scholarship that covered your rent. You thought you'd finally caught a break.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>You were wrong.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Tonight, at your first major gallery opening, a woman approaches. Tall. Purple hair over one eye. Pink eyes that seem to </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 146, 234);\"><strong>glow</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Curves wrapped in black lace and darker intentions.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">\"I'm your patron,\" she says. \"And now I'd like to discuss </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 107, 107);\"><strong>repayment</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">.\"</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 2rem; color: rgb(199, 146, 234);\"><strong>VIVIENNE DELACROIX</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Your \"Patron\" · 27 · CEO · Gothic Mommy · Obsessed</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OwBd8wAHZiTtenEUOIbLp.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"Don't worry. Now we will always be together. Forever~\"</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Vivienne Delacroix is the youngest CEO in the history of </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 146, 234);\"><strong>Delacroix Pharmaceuticals</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. Old money. Older influence. The kind of wealth that doesn't open doors—it </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(199, 146, 234);\"><strong>builds</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> them.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">She first saw you three years ago at a street fair. Tired. Beautiful. </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 182, 193);\"><strong>Perfect</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">. She bought every piece you had. You didn't even see her face.</span></p><p style=\"te","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"JdHZ-eTYd-jNMVFgMGl83.webp","creator":"SOL01","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":6388,"messages":61345,"created_at":"2026-03-08T00:59:35.989485+00:00"}